* Patterns
** Set disance between flexbox items.
Not super elegant, but this works.
#+BEGIN_SRC css
  .flexbox {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .flexbox > div {
    /*
      1/3  - 3 columns per row
      10px - spacing between columns 
    ,*/
    box-sizing: border-box;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    outline: 1px dotted red;
    width: calc(1/3*100% - (1 - 1/3)*10px);-
    /*
      Also can be simplified as: 
      width:calc(1/3*100% - 5px);
     ,*/
  }
#+END_SRC
